titles.title: A resolution commemorating the 80th anniversary of the establishment of the Missisquoi National Wildlife Refuge.
A resolution commemorating the 80th anniversary of the establishment of the Missisquoi National Wildlife Refuge.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Environment and Public Works.

bill.summary: This resolution commemorates the 80th anniversary of the establishment of the Missisquoi National Wildlife Refuge and recognizes the importance of this protected land to biodiversity and fragile ecosystems in Vermont and the world.
